{
  "stem": "21786.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If one read the newspaper, which was by that point [GERMAN], meaning everything along the line of the party-- so the Czech newspaper became, I mean, just the mouthpiece of the German newspapers.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the Jews were the favorite target of any misery or anything, whatever that went wrong.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the Jews became the same type of theoretically vermin-- as in the German nomenclature.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then we had to give away-- which, at that point, didn't mean anything to me, with one little exception-- anything from precious metals, anything which would be antique, any kind of fur, any kind of heavy coat, any kind of--",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Everything.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everything what I just mentioned.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I gave away stamp collection, and you can-- if you had any kind of silver, gold, cutlery, I mean, more valuable china-- which was specifically named.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And finally, I had to give away my violin, which really hit me badly.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was gathering places, simply, where you had to bring it to this gathering place, and you got a specific kind of list what you gave there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And if you wouldn't, so the penalty was quite clear cut.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Simply, the penalty was imprisonment, and probably concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Interestingly enough, the Czech population looked aside.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Czech population-- the great majority simply didn't denounce anyone.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were-- to be denounced by a Czech, it was an absolute rarity.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was naturally a small segment of Czech fascists.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But it was a real exception.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Like, I met-- the first time, really, when I felt that something is going really wrong, I met one former classmate who actually failed from the gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "His name was Bozanovak, B-O-Z-A-N-O-V-A-K.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We had already stars at that point.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We got-- the order came to have Stars of David, with the Jude on it, Jew.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
